=head1 DESCRIPTION

The tag specifications of an Amazon EBS volume.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 PropagateTags => Str

Determines whether to propagate the tags from the task definition to
the Amazon EBS volume. Tags can only propagate to a C<SERVICE>
specified in C<ServiceVolumeConfiguration>. If no value is specified,
the tags aren't propagated.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ResourceType => Str

The type of volume resource.


=head2 Tags => ArrayRef[L<Paws::ECS::Tag>]

The tags applied to this Amazon EBS volume. C<AmazonECSCreated> and
C<AmazonECSManaged> are reserved tags that can't be used.



